Class MockBindRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.grapht.solver.MockBindRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<BindRule>, BindRule

    public class MockBindRule
extends Object
implements BindRule
    MockBindRule is a simple implementation of BindRule where the matching bindings are represented as a map from input Desires to output Desires, via addMapping(Desire, Desire).
